## Key Insights
Raft tolerates (N-1)/2 failures via leader election and majority quorum. Hybrid Raft/Paxos protocols could optimize read latency.

## Connections
Raft strict majority vs. Paxos flexibility represents a design trade-off.

## Foundation
Well-established: Raft consensus, Paxos flexible quorums.

## Open Questions
When does strict majority cause unnecessary unavailability?